casebody.data:
RPOST COMMUNICATIONS LIMITED, et al., petitioners,
v.
GODADDY.COM, LLC. No. 17-695. Supreme Court of the United States Dec. 11, 2017.

Motion of DiMora Mobile, LLC for leave to file a brief as amicus curiae granted. Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Federal Circuit denied.
